title: Flip.Men.Season.2.HDTV.XviD
description:
Follow Utah-based real estate investors, Doug 
Clark and Mike Baird as they attempt to turn run 
down properties into profit. After a fierce daily 
bidding war at auction, the duo acquires a 
home, sight unseen, meaning when they 
first enter their newly purchased house, they never 
know what will be waiting behind the door. Will 
it be a biohazard, a meth lab, or an angry former 
tenant who just doesn't want to leave? Doug 
and Mike then have to clean up the place,
 renovate it, stage it, get it to market, and flip
 it...fast. It's a race against time, because every
 day means thousands of dollars out of their
 pocket. They're the ultimate prospectors, and
 the stakes couldn't be higher.
